## Error Recovery

| Error | Recovery |
|-------|---------|
| CI lint/type failure | Auto-fix, commit, re-run |
| Git conflict | Report to user |
| Scope creep (diff outside contract) | Revert, re-read contract |
| Import/permission error | Fix deps or report |

Same error after 2 retries → log to `build-notes.md`, proceed to next deliverable.

### Recovery after interruption

`harness session read --task <task-id>` + `harness handoff read --task <task-id>` → resume from exact step. Do not recap or apologize.
